  "description": [
    "The Frontier PUBLISHED EVERY THURSDAY BY TUK FRONTIER PRINTING COMPANY D H CRONIN Editor Good moruiug Havo you laid in your supply of war bonds yet Another Spanish fleet is on move but there is no such good luck as its moving far in this direction There will be more bond holders in this country after thoso war bonds are issued than ever before General Shaftkr and his boys will now give the world an exhibi tion of what they can do in the hero producing liue It is reasonably certain that the senate as well as the house will be controlled by the republicans after the 4th of next March The democrats in congress are acting as though they wished the congressional elections to be unani mousfor the republicans Thebe are now U S soldiers in the Phillipines to aid Dewey in driving oat the last vestige of Span ish authority on the islands Ir old man Leiter pays four or five million dollars for his boys ex perience without making faces we dont figure that any kick is coming to anybody else The middleoftheroaders pop ulists have issued a call for a national convention to be held at"
